13th consecutive year, the Marjorie Ryan Circle of
ACC—Advocacy and Caring for Children (formerly
known as the Association for Catholic Childhood) will
be selling the finest quality Northwest 22" mixed Noble
Fir wreaths for $20 each. We will also offer locally
grown, stunning red or white 6” poinsettias for $15
each. All proceeds from this sale go directly to the
charitable local children's organizations that ACC
supports. Order for yourself, or as gifts for family and
friends. Download the order form from the Cathedral
website, <a target="_bulletin" href="http://www.stjames-cathedral.org">www.stjames-cathedral.org</a>.
<i>Information</i>,
<a href="mailto:gayle@kaplan1.com?subject=Christmas Wreath and Poinsettia Sale">
Gayle Kaplan</a>.</p>
