<p><b>A WEEKLY TIP ON CARING FOR OUR COMMON HOME</b>.
Buy used items whenever feasible, and if possible
repair rather than replace broken items. In most cases
this will save money, but it also will preserve resources
and reduce overall consumption.</p>
